0escalation.%20But%20it's%20both%3A%20there's%20a%20long-standing%20pattern%2C%20and%20then%20there%20are%20also%20certain%20things%20that%20have%20happened%20recently%20that%20suggest%20an%20escalation%20and%20certainly%20have%20hallmarks%20of%20authoritarianism%2C%20and%20fascism%20%E2%80%94%20the%20various%20-isms.%20So%20certainly%2C%20these%20comments%20would%20fit%20that%20here%20as%20far%20as%20the%20vermi%2Cn%20but%20they%20are%20not%20really%20that%20much%20different%20in%20many%20respects%20from%20his%20prior%20references%20to%20infestations%20that%20go%20back%20quite%20a%20ways%20actually%2C%20long%20before%20his%20political%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20give%20me%20examples%20of%20times%20his%20phrasing%20touched%20on%20those%20troubling%20themes%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertainly%2C%20within%20terms%20of%20his%20political%20career%2C%20the%20use%20of%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Binfest%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Binfestation%26quot%3B%20is%20pretty%20substantial%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20different%20contexts%20that%20he's%20used%20it%20to%20refer%20to%20immigrants%2C%20MS-13%20specifically%2C%20and%20people%20in%20predominantly%20African%20American%20parts%20of%20Baltimore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20members%20of%20Congress%2C%20women%20of%20color%2C%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tells-progressive-congresswomen-to-go-back-to-their-countries-aoc-ilhan-omar-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego%20back%20to%20the%20crime-infested%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20they%20came%20from.%20More%20recently%20there's%20also%20this%20comment%20about%20his%20political%20opponents%20being%20vermin%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20also%20as%20it%20relates%20to%20things%20he's%20been%20saying%20he'd%20do%20if%20he%20were%20to%20be%20reelected%2C%20like%20what%20they're%20planning%20to%20do%20with%20Department%20of%20Justice.%20You%20can%20also%20look%20at%20some%20of%20the%20things%20he%20said%20he'd%2