essman%20Patrick%20Moynihan%2C%20who%20was%20also%20a%20sociologist%2C%20wrote%20about%20in%20the%20early%2090s.%20It%20was%20this%20idea%20that%2C%20at%20certain%20points%20in%20time%2C%20deviance%20can%20have%20a%20higher%20or%20lower%20threshold%20for%20how%20it's%20defined.%20And%20that%20definition%20is%20subjected%20to%20all%20kinds%20of%20contextual%20situational%20factors.%20Historical%20factors%20will%20affect%20how%20we%20view%20deviance%20as%20it%20relates%20to%20a%20particular%20person.%20I%20think%20that's%20exactly%20what's%20happened%20with%20Trump%2C%20is%20that%20deviance%20has%20been%20defined%20down%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20there's%20so%20much%20focus%20on%2C%20it's%20almost%20like%20an%20overload%20of%20sorts.%20The%20result%20is%2C%20you%20just%20don't%20see%20it%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20almost%20like%20he's%20kind%20of%20normalizing%20this%20on%20some%20level.%20Even%20as%20outrageous%20as%20he%20can%20be%2C%20it's%20been%20very%20difficult%2C%20I%20think%2C%20for%20people%20to%20maintain%20a%20consistent%20vigilance%20and%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-the-most-anti-democratic-president-in-modern-us-history-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20threat%20that%20he%20represents%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it's%20kind%20of%20overwhelming%2C%20really%2C%20in%20many%20respects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20it%20has%20to%20be%20a%20remarkably%20negative%20comment%20or%20some%20kind%20of%20plan%20of%20action%20he%20says%20to%20even%20register%20as%20out%20of%20character%20for%20him%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that's%20really%20remarkable%20about%20his%20record%20is%20that%20he's%20been%20able%20to%20consistently%20promote%20violence%20over%20many%20years%2C%20and%20that%20hasn't%20been%20a%20dealbreaker.%20Within%20the%20context%20of%20conventional%20politics%2C%20just%20one%20instance%20of%20advocating%20for%20violence%2C%20I%20think%2C%20in%20many%20cases%20would%20end%20a%20person's%20career%2C%20but%20he's%20been%20able%20to%20do%20that%20repeatedly.%20Like%20the%20whole%20classic%20line%20he%20had%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-joke-shoot-somebody-2016-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estanding%20on%20Fifth%20Avenue%20and%20shooting%20someone%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20he%20would%20still%20maintain%20their%20support.%20It's%20just%20very%20inconsistent%20with%20what%20I%20think%20would%20often%20happen%20if%20a%20typical%20politician%20suggested%20something%20along%20those%20lines%20in%20terms%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20what%20do%20you%20attribute%20that%20to%3F%20From%20your%20perspective%2C%20is%20there%20something%20that%20he%20could%20do%20that%20would%20change%20the%20tides%20for%20his%20supporters%2C%20or%20do%20you%20think%20he's%20right%20in%20saying%20that%20there's%20not%20a%20lot%20that%20he%20could%20do%20to%20shake%20their%20support%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20mean%2C%20there's%20always%20going%20to%20be%20some%20percentage%20of%20folks%20that%20come%20and%20go%20in%20terms%20of%20support%20with%20a%20leader%20like%20this%2C%20but%20he%20does%20seem%20to%20have%20a%20core%20base%20that's%20been%20pretty%20resilient.%20They%20maintain%20their%20support%20for%20him%20and%20it's%20hard%2C%20at%20this%20point%2C%20to%20see%20what%20it%20would%20take%20to%20change%20that%20for%20the%20core%20base%20of%20true%20believers%20who%20are%20unwavering%20and%20fully%20committed%20in%20his%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20not%20all%20of%20those%20who%20support%20Trump%3B%20there%20is%20there%20is%20some%20kind%20of%20variability%20there.%20We%20have%20seen%20that%20people%20no%20longer%20support%20him%20at%20various%20points%2C%20whether%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-obstruction-case-donald-trump-january-6-riot-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJanuary%206%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20otherwise.%20There%20has%20been%20some%20layer%20that%20gets%20peeled%20off%2C%20but%20there%20does%20seem%20to%20be%20a%20core%20of%20these%20unwavering%20folks%20that%20makes%20it%20hard%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20it%20would%20take%20for%20them%20to%20no%20longer%20support%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20makes%20you%20sure%20Trump's%20rhetoric%20is%20tangible%20evidence%20of%20an%20authoritarian%20ideology%2C%20rather%20than%20us%20just%20piecing%20together%20scraps%20and%20trying%20to%20make%20them%20fit%20that%20narrative%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20what%20gives%20it%20its%20greatest%20degree%20of%20tangibility%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20are%20so%20many%20different%20puzzle%20pieces%20that%20fit%20very%20closely.%20We're%20not%20stretching%20things%20here%3B%20the%20pieces%20are%20all%20there%20and%20closely%20connected%2C%20in%20some%20cases%20already%20connected.%20And%20that%20does%20make%20it%20very%20tangible.%20I%20think%20that's%20something%20that's%20difficult%20to%20deal%20with%3B%20like%20when%20he%20says%20these%20things%20and%20does%20these%20things%2C%20it%20might%20be%20similar%20to%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Finternational-teenage-neo-nazi-network-feuerkrieg-totenwaffen-accelerationism-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efar-right%20extremists%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Efascists%2C%20and%20authoritarians%20do%2C%20but%20there's%20still%20a%20degree%20of%20removal%20in%20people's%20minds%20between%20what%20he's%20saying%20and%20doing%20and%20those%20ideas%20in%20these%20constructs.%20And%20that's%20in%20part%20because%20we%20have%20an%20image%20in%20our%20head%20of%20what%20those%20things%20look%20like%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20our%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20you're%20saying%20that%20because%20he%20doesn't%20look%20like%20what%20we%20imagine%20an%20authoritarian%20or%20fascist%20to%20look%20like%2C%20people%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20labeling%20him%20as%20one%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%2C%20whether%20we're%20talking%20about%20far-right%20extremism%20or%20white%20supremacy%2C%20authoritarianism%20or%20fascism%2C%20whichever%20construct%20you%20want%20to%20use%20here%2C%20these%20are%20things%20that%20people%20%E2%80%94%20regular%20people%20%E2%80%94%20embody.%20But%20I%20think%20we%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20stereotypical%20ideas%20about%20what%20white%20supremacy%20looks%20like%20because%20in%20the%20United%20States%20history%20with%20groups%20like%20the%20Klan%2C%20there's%20white%20sheets%20or%20there's%20shaved%20heads%20and%20swastikas.%20And%20those%20are%20all%20things%20that%2C%20yeah%2C%20sure%2C%20are%20real%20indicators%2C%20but%20you%20can%20have%20white%20supremacy%20without%20any%20of%20those%20things%20being%20present.%20So%20I%20think%20we're%20a%20little%20confused%20when%20we%20see%20authoritarianism%2C%20fascism%2C%20white%20supremacy%2C%20and%20far-right%20extremism.%20We%20expect%20to%20see%20certain%20markers%2C%20and%20if%20we%20don't%20see%20those%20things%2C%20then%20those%20concepts%20seem%20farther%20removed%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20there's%20lots%20of%20evidence%20that's%20consistent%20with%20that%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-rhetoric-mirroring-nazi-fascism-hitler-expert-warns-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704020221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655b802222cf74a5739a19b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-rhetoric-mirroring-nazi-fascism-hitler-expert-warns-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Extremism%20expert%20Peter%20Simi%20told%20Business%20Insider%20why%20Donald%20Trump's%20increasingly%20extreme%20rhetoric%20keeps%20falling%20on%20deaf%20ears.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsid