0prop%20it%2C%20what%20wonder%20that%20the%20media%20should%20have%20flashed%20it%20as%20unrelentingly%20continuous%20fare%20on%20television%2C%20no%20holds%20barred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20culmination%20of%20the%20politics%20here%20is%20the%20stunningly%20audacious%20call%20given%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20that%20the%20nation%20celebrate%20Diwali%20on%20January%2022%20of%20the%20new%20year%20when%20the%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20is%20due%20to%20be%20consecrated%20and%20installed%20in%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20of%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoes%20it%20seem%20sacrilegious%20that%20Modi%20should%20have%20made%20bold%20to%20rearrange%20the%20hallowed%20sanatan%20calendar%20of%20holy%20days%20rather%20to%20suit%20the%20political%20purposes%20of%20the%20right-wing%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20there%20a%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emahant%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20town%20who%20might%20make%20bold%20to%20point%20out%20to%20the%20chief%20executive%20of%20the%20as%20yet%20non-denominational%20government%20that%20it%20is%20not%20for%20him%20to%20recast%20the%20time%20of%20day%20on%20the%20calendar%20when%20Lord%20Ram%20is%20understood%20to%20have%20returned%20to%20the%20kingdom%20of%20Ayodhya%20after%20his%2014%20years%20of%20exile%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20unchallenged%20seems%20now%20the%20sway%20of%20the%20Modi%20cult%20that%20the%20Bonapartist%20edict%20to%20celebrate%20Diwali%20some%20nine%20months%20before%20the%20sanatan%20calendar%20warrants%20it%20may%20come%20to%20be%20lapped%20up%20with%20fervour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThinking%20back%2C%20what%20church%20after%20all%20had%20the%20guts%20to%20stand%20%C2%A0up%20to%20Henry%20VIII%2C%20when%20he%20sought%20sanction%20for%20the%20annulment%20of%20his%20marriage%20with%20Katherine%20of%20Aragon%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20our%20Tudor%20days%20are%20here.%20So%20why%20can%E2%80%99t%20Diwali%20%C2%A0be%20celebrated%20nine%20months%20before%20it%20is%20due%20if%20doing%20so%20helps%20hasten%20our%20leap%20to%20global%