espect%20to%20the%20gett.%20It%20also%20creates%20a%20monetary%20incentive%20for%20a%20spouse%20to%20give%20the%20gett.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20least%20it's%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20Haart%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20a%20downside%3A%20the%20approach%20is%20preventative%20and%20it%20doesn't%20help%20women%20already%20in%20marriages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20women%20trapped%20in%20marriages%20without%20prenups%2C%20activists%20are%20instead%20focusing%20on%20introducing%20state-level%20laws%20to%20classify%20gett%20refusal%20as%20coercive%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20will%20be%20a%20really%20brilliant%20way%20to%20use%20American%20laws%20to%20force%20these%20people%20to%20release%20these%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20Haart%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20gett%20can't%20technically%20be%20forced%20under%20Jewish%20law%2C%20because%20it%20becomes%20invalid%20if%20either%20party%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20acting%20under%20duress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Keshet%20Starr%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20ORA%2C%20said%20there%20is%20still%20value%20in%20the%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20of%20us%20working%20in%20the%20field%20to%20help%20agunot%20know%20very%20clearly%20that%20gett%20refusal%20is%20a%20form%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsex-relationships%2Fdomestic-abuse%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edomestic%20abuse%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20one%20spouse%20manipulates%20and%20weaponizes%20the%20Jewish%20divorce%20process%20to%20control%20his%20or%20her%20partner%2C%26quot%3B%20Starr%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCoercive%20control%20legislation%20is%20one%20important%20way%20to%20make%20sure%20our%20legal%20system%20understands%20this%20critical%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMaking%20it%20a%20Class-E%20Felony%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmber%20Adler%20was%20an%20agunah%20for%20two%20years.%20She%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20she%20was%20made%20to%20%3