%20send%20a%20powerful%20message%20to%20gett-refusers%2C%20Adler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-manchester-60957813%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elandmark%20case%20in%20the%20UK%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20put%20the%20use%20of%20such%20legislation%20to%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlan%20Moher%20was%20sentenced%20to%2018%20months%20in%20prison%20for%20controlling%20or%20coercive%20behavior%20after%20he%20refused%20to%20grant%20a%20gett%20to%20his%20wife%2C%20Caroline%20Moher-Maxwell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Julia%20Haart%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570d5f20ec98e92f74ce0d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJulia%20Haart%3Cp%3EClark%20Hodgin%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Haart%2C%20it's%20a%20hopeful%20sign%20that%2C%20with%20the%20right%20laws%20in%20place%2C%20women%20like%20the%20ones%20she%20knew%20back%20in%20Monsey%20might%20one%20day%20be%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20saying%20that%20truly%20things%20are%20never%20going%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20before%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20actually%20believed%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20doing%20the%20work%20that%20I%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch4%3EPhoto%20Credits%3A%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Ch6%3EPhotography%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20Clark%20Hodgin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh6%3E%3Ch6%3ELighting%20Assistance%3A%20Conor%20Cunningham%3C%2Fh6%3E%3Ch6%3EHair%3A%20Tiffany%2F%20L'%20Appartement%20Hair%20Boudoir%20TN%20Group%3C%2Fh6%3E%3Ch6%3EMakeup%3A%20Asami%20Matsuda%2FSaint%20Luke%20Artists%3C%2Fh6%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjulia-haart-myunorthodoxlife-netflix-end-gett-crisis-chained-women-jewish-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv