C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20flew%20on%20a%20Loganair%20flight%20from%20Glasgow%20to%20Barra%20Airport%2C%20the%20only%20airport%20in%20the%20world%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fflight-glasgow-to-barra-scotland-tiny-plane-journey-pictures-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunway%20on%20the%20beach%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20was%20magical%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20that%20I%20had%20arrived%20in%20a%20tropical%20destination%20thanks%20to%20the%20sunny%20weather%20which%20made%20the%20white%20sandy%20beach%20look%20picturesque.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20beach%20looked%20completely%20different%20before%20the%20flight%20back%20to%20Glasgow.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22passengers%20walk%20towards%20a%20plane%20on%20a%20beach%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658efcd3ab6f2ebb11f7c450%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221530%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPassengers%20walk%20towards%20the%20plane.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Scotland%2C%20the%20weather%20is%20ever-changing%20and%20we%20often%20joke%20that%20we%20have%20four%20seasons%20in%20one%20day.%20But%20even%20so%2C%20I%20was%20stunned%20by%20the%20airport%20beach's%20gloomy%20transformation%20when%20it%20was%20time%20to%20travel%20back%20to%20Glasgow%20two%20days%20later.%20The%20sky%20was%20cloudy%2C%20the%20sea%20was%20gray%2C%20and%20tourists%20were%20wrapped%20up%20in%20puffy%20jackets%20and%20hats%20as%20they%20posed%20for%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20incredibly%20windy%2C%20and%20we%20were%20told%20that%20the%20flight%20could%20have%20been%20canceled%20if%20the%20strong%20winds%20continued%20(thankfully%2C%20it%20wasn't).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20thistle%20is%20Scotland's%20national%20flower%2C%20so%20I%20was%20hoping%20to%20find%20some%20on%20Barra's%20beaches.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222719%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Scottish%20thistles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658d92ddab6f2ebb11f75ec2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221809%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScottish%20thistles.%3Cp%3Etirc83%2FGetty%20Unages%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThistles%20are%20small%2C%20bristled%20plants%20that%20often%20have%20a%20purple%20or%20blue%20flower.%20A%20patriotic%20symbol%2C%20the%20thistle's%20connection%20to%20Scotland%20dates%20back%20to%201470%2C%20when%20an%20illustration%20of%20one%20appeared%20on%20coins%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.visitscotland.com%2Finspiration%2Fculture%2Fthistle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVisit%20Scotland%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThistles%20are%20common%20where%20I%20live%20in%20Glasgow.%20But%20even%20so%2C%20I%20was%20excited%20about%20the%20prospect%20of%20photographing%20the%20flower%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Scotland's%20islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20I%20made%20the%20mistake%20of%20visiting%20in%20September%2C%20when%20some%20thistles%20were%20already%20dead.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dead%20thistles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658d93e21c5c7b8c9a0c828e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDead%20thistles%20are%20pictured%20on%20a%20beach%20in%20Barra.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20I%20photographed%20some%20purple%20thistles%20during%20my%20trip%2C%20many%20had%20already%20lost%20their%20color%20and%20were%20wilted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThistles%20are%20most%20commonly%20seen%20between%20July%20and%20September%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rhs.org.uk%2Fweeds%2Fcreeping-thistle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERoyal%20Horticultural%20Society%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20UK's%20leading%20gardening%20charity.%20Next%20time%2C%20I'll%20visit%20earlier%20in%20the%20year%20to%20ensure%20my%20chances%20of%20seeing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAlso%20on%20Barra%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20that%20many%20local%20businesses%20weren't%20open%20full-time.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22barra%20local%20business%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658eec39ab6f2ebb11f7b5d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELocal%20businesses%20in%20Barra%20weren't%20open%20full-time.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20trip%20to%20Barra%20overlapped%20with%20the%20offseason%2C%20which%20lasts%20from%20the%20end%20of%20September%20until%20May.%20I%20didn't%20think%20this%20was%20important%20when%20I%20initially%20booked%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20locals%20informed%20me%20that%20many%20restaurants%20and%20hotels%20close%20when%20tourists%20leave%20in%20the%20winter%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20some%20benefits%20to%20traveling%20during%20the%20offseason.%20For%20example%2C%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhy-you-should-travel-to-scottish-islands-during-off-season-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20only%20guests%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20Isle%20of%20Barra%20Beach%20Hotel%20before%20it%20closed%20for%20the%20winter.%20The%20staff%20were%20lovely%2C%20and%20we%20were%20treated%20like%20VIPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20open%20businesses%20also%20made%20us%20feel%20like%20we%20were%20in%20a%20ghost%20town.%20Understandably%2C%20many%20businesses%20didn't%20stay%20open%20all%20day%20like%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fvisit-scotland-mistakes-tourists-make-glasgow-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20home%20city%2C%20Glasgow%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Service-based%20businesses%20only%20accepted%20appointments%2C%20while%20others%20had%20reduced%20operating%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBefore%20visiting%20Easdale%20Island%2C%20I%20envisioned%20rolling%20hills%20and%20quaint%20cottages.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224133%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20flooded%20slate%20quarries%20on%20Easdale%20Island%2C%20Scotland.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658eeeacec62ab5daf7f8e04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223100%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20aerial%20view%20of%20flooded%20slate%20quarries%20on%20Easdale%20Island%2C%20Scotland.%3Cp%3EIain%20Masterton%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20visiting%20Barra%2C%20my%20next%20destination%20was%20Seil%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fphotos-what-its-like-to-travel-easdale-scottish-island-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEasdale%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20neighboring%20slate%20islands%20in%20the%20Inner%20Hebrides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeil%20is%20connected%20to%20the%20mainland%20via%20a%20bridge%20and%20has%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.argyll-bute.gov.uk%2Fmy-community%2Fpopulation-where-we-live%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E550%20residents%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhile%20Easdale%20is%20reachable%20via%20ferry%20and%20has%20only%2060%20residents%2C%20according%20to%20its%20website.%20I%20was%20particularly%20excited%20to%20visit%20Easdale%20due%20to%20its%20small%20size%3B%20the%20island%20has%20one%20pub%20and%20restaurant%20but%20no%20grocery%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20island%20is%20beautiful%2C%20filled%20with%20rolling%20green%20hills%2C%20views%20of%20the%20sea%2C%20and%20cozy%20cream%20cottages.%20I%20couldn't%20wait%20to%20see%20it%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESimilarly%20to%20Barra%2C%20the%20weather%20in%20Easdale%20was%20dreary%20during%20my%20visit.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221629%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22easdale%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658eeee1ec62ab5daf7f8e15%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221222%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20island%20was%20beautiful.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEasdale%20was%20beautiful%2C%20but%20I%20found%20visiting%20slightly%20uncomfortable%20due%20to%20the%20stormy%20weather.%20As%20you%20would%20expect%2C%20there%20aren't%20many%20local%20businesses%20on%20the%20island%20and%20no%20cars%2C%20so%20most%20activities%20are%20outdoor-based%20and%20involve%20walking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20time%2C%20I'll%20be%20sure%20to%20visit%20earlier%20in%20the%20summer%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20the%20good%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20had%20been%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20ferry%20journey%20to%20Easdale.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22small%20boat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658d98f9ab6f2ebb11f76211%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221494%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20small%20boat%20is%20pictured%20closed%20to%20Easdale%20Island.%3Cp%3Ekodachrome25%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEasdale%20is%20accessible%20via%20a%20three-minute%20ferry%20journey%20from%20Seil%2C%20and%20round-trip%20tickets%20cost%20%C2%A32.20%2C%20or%20about%20%242.80%2C%20per%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20ferry%20was%20open%20and%20exposed%20to%20the%20elements.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221567%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mikhaila%20easdale%20ferry%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658efec3ec62ab5daf7f99cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221175%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMikhaila%20Friel%20pictured%20on%20the%20ferry%20to%20Easdale%20Island.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20visiting%20Easdale%2C%20I%20had%20spoken%20to%20some%20islanders%20who%20said%20there%20are%20regular%20ferry%20services%20to%20and%20from%20the%20island%20on%20a%20small%20ferry%20that%20can%20hold%2010%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20partner%20and%20I%20were%20the%20only%20passengers%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20two%20ferrymen%2C%20who%20were%20dressed%20in%20waterproof%20clothing.%20I%20was%20glad%20I%20remembered%20to%20bring%20a%20waterproof%20jacket%2C%20as%20there%20was%20no%20cover%20on%20the%20ferry%2C%20and%20the%20rainy%20weather%20meant%20the%20seats%20were%20drenched.%20I%20didn't%20see%20any%20covered%20ferries%20during%20my%20visit%2C%20so%20those%20traveling%20to%20Easdale%20should%20be%20prepared%20for%20all%20kinds%20of%20weather%20on%20a%20ferry%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUpon%20arriving%20at%20the%20island%2C%20I%20noticed%20a%20handful%20of%20people%20waiting%20for%20the%20next%20ferry%20back%20to%20Seil.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221891%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22line%20for%20the%20ferry%20on%20Easdale%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658eeff9ec62ab5daf7f8e7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221418%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20line%20of%20people%20waiting%20for%20the%20ferry.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20trip%20to%20Easdale%20fell%20on%20the%20same%20day%20as%20the%20World%20Stone%20Skimming%20Championships%2C%20a%20contest%20hosted%20annually%20on%20the%20island%20that%20is%20open%20to%20people%20from%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%2C%20the%20championships%20were%20just%20wrapping%20up%2C%20and%20I%20noticed%20lines%20of%20people%20waiting%20in%20the%20rain%20for%20the%20ferry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20ferry%20can%20only%20hold%2010%20people%2C%20I%20can%20imagine%20that%20some%20people%20probably%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20a%20while%20during%20busy%20periods.%20Thankfully%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20long%20upon%20my%20return%20to%20Seil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20island's%20only%20pub%20was%20surprisingly%20busy%20during%20the%20offseason.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mikhaila%20pictured%20on%20easdale%20island%20pub%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658ef0aa1c5c7b8c9a0cd963%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20island's%20only%20pub%20was%20overcrowded.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20family-owned%20Puffer%20Bar%20and%20Cafe%20was%20just%20a%20short%20walk%20from%20where%20the%20ferry%20dropped%20me%20off.%20When%20I%20arrived%2C%20the%20pub%20was%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20assumed%20the%20pub%20was%20busy%20because%20of%20the%20World%20Stone%20Skimming%20Championships%2C%20but%20one%20local%20told%20me%20that%20most%20of%20the%20competitors%20had%20already%20gone%20home%20and%20mostly%20locals%20were%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20atmosphere%20was%20lively%20and%20friendly%20and%20I%20could%20see%20why%20people%20wanted%20to%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20still%20had%20an%20amazing%20time%2C%20but%20if%20I%20were%20to%20island-hop%20in%20the%20future%2C%20I'd%20avoid%20the%20offseason.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Easdale%20Island%20in%20the%20rain%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658ef169ab6f2ebb11f7b8a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20is%20pictured%20on%20Easdale%20Island%20in%20the%20rain.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBarra%2C%20Seil%2C%20and%20Easdale%20were%20unforgettable%20destinations%2C%20and%20each%20island%20had%20its%20own%20distinct%20charm.%20I'm%20grateful%20I%20got%20to%20experience%20island-hopping%2C%20but%20next%20time%