trality%20in%20the%20world%20oil%20market%20is%20the%20centerpiece%20of%20Saudi%20global%20influence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gause.%20%26quot%3BThe%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20disrupted%20energy%20markets%20and%20drove%20prices%20up%20in%202022%2C%20increased%20Riyadh's%20relevance%20for%20the%20countries%20like%20the%20US%20that%20had%20distanced%20themselves%20from%20MBS.%C2%A0%20If%20you%20want%20to%20do%20business%20with%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20you%20need%20to%20do%20business%20with%20the%20Crown%20Prince.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20major%20economies%2C%20such%20as%20China%20or%20Russia%2C%20which%20don't%20share%20US%20concerns%20over%20human%20rights%20violations%2C%20had%20expressed%20no%20concern%20over%20the%20Khashoggi%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jamal%20Khashoggi%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5bbc22bdae84ee170d439a03%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJamal%20Khashoggi%20is%20featured%20on%20a%20poster%20during%20a%20protest%20organized%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Turkish-Arabic%20Media%20Association%20at%20the%20entrance%20to%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20consulate%20on%20October%208%2C%202018%20in%20Istanbul%2C%20Turkey.%3Cp%3EChris%20McGrath%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20it%20was%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20that%20brought%20the%20Biden%20Administration%20around%20to%20dealing%20with%20MBS%2C%20most%20other%20countries%2C%20including%20Russia%20and%20China%2C%20had%20been%20dealing%20with%20Riyadh%20without%20any%20problems%20or%20interruptions%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECanny%20diplomacy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECrown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20has%20used%20not%20just%20used%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20economic%20might%2C%20but%20canny%20diplomacy%20to%20win%20back%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20has%20entered%20into%20US-brokered%20negotiations%20to%20normalize%20relations%20with%20Israel%2C%20though%20these%20were%20abruptly%20halted%20by%20the%20Hamas%20terror%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20and%20the%20subsequent%20Israeli%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Saudis%20have%20also%20engaged%20in%20China-brokered%20discussions%20to%20ease%20tensions%20with%20Iran%2C%20its%20regional%20arch-enemy%2C%20and%20back%20away%20from%20the%20conflict%20in%20Yemen%2C%20where%20Saudi%20and%20Iran-backed%20proxies%20are%20engaged%20in%20a%20brutal%20and%20protracted%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaudi%20efforts%20to%20stabilize%20a%20region%20that%20has%20been%20racked%20by%20decades%20of%20conflict%20and%20sectarian%20strife%20are%20tied%20to%20the%20crown%20prince's%20determination%20to%20reshape%20the%20Saudi%20economy%2C%20say%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSaudi%20Arabia%20has%20become%20a%20more%20consequential%20and%20constructive%20player%20in%20Middle%20East%20affairs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jon%20Alterman%20of%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%20%26quot%3BSaudi%20Arabia%20is%20doing%20more%20hard%20things%20simultaneously%20than%20it%20has%20ever%20done%20before%2C%20and%20it%20is%20doing%20so%20more%20effectively%20than%20it%20has%20ever%20done%20before.%20That%20has%20helped%20improve%20the%20crown%20prince's%20standing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20has%20subsided%2C%20Saudi%20will%20likely%20resume%20the%20process%20of%20attempting%20to%20normalize%20ties%20with%20Israel%2C%20said%20Gause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20the%20crisis%20ends%2C%20the%20factors%20that%20drove%20that%20process%20will%20come%20back%20into%20play%20%E2%80%93%20joint%20Saudi%20and%20Israeli%20worries%20about%20Iran%2C%20the%20Saudi%20desire%20for%20a%20codified%20security%20guarantee%20from%20the%20US%2C%20the%20Biden%20Administration's%20insistence%20that%20such%20a%20guarantee%20can%20only%20come%20as%20part%20of%20a%20Saudi-Israeli%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alterman.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crown%20prince%20isn't%20restricting%20himself%20to%20winning%20over%20political%20and%20business%20leaders%2C%20but%20is%20seeking%20to%20broadly%20rehabilitate%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20image%20in%20the%20West%20as%20he%20seeks%20investment%20and%20encourages%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESportswashing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20pursuit%20of%20this%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20is%20turning%20itself%20into%20a%20global%20sports%20superpower%20as%20part%20of%20its%20so%3Cs%3E-%3C%2Fs%3Ecalled%20%26quot%3Bsportswashing%26quot%3B%20strategy.%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund%20has%20invested%20billions%20in%20PGA%20golf%2C%20hosting%20heavyweight%20boxing%20tournaments%2C%20and%20bringing%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20famous%20soccer%20players%20to%20compete%20in%20its%20domestic%20league.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20obstacles%20remain%20for%20the%20crown%20prince%20in%20his%20quest%20to%20cement%20and%20expand%20his%20global%20influence%20%E2%80%94%20not%20least%20his%20continued%20determination%20to%20crush%20dissent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20he%20has%20launched%20a%20campaign%20to%20punish%20critics%20of%20his%20Neom%20megacity%20project.%20Business%20Insider%20in%20August%20reported%20that%20Saudi%20authorities%20had%20jailed%20a%20series%20of%20dissidents%20for%20up%20to%2030%20years%20in%20punishment%20for%20questioning%20the%20decision%20by%20Saudi%20authorities%20to%20forcibly%20oust%20people%20living%20on%20land%20where%20the%20city%20will%20be%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20crown%20prince's%20authoritarian%20instincts%20and%20impulsiveness%20again%20lead%20him%20to%20punish%20a%20critic%20beyond%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20border%2C%20relations%20with%20the%20US%20could%20again%20go%20into%20tailspin%2C%20and%20the%20kingdom's%20glossy%20new%20image%20could%20be%20irreparably%20tarnished.%