an%20ji%3F%E2%80%9D%20Constable%20Awdhesh%20Rana%20called%20out%20to%20Rahman%20miyan%20as%20he%20strode%20into%20the%20restaurant.%20Kanwal%2C%20the%20pillion%20rider%2C%20walked%20in%20behind%20him%2C%20smirking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20saying%20to%20Kanwal%20ji%20that%20I%20will%20take%20you%20for%20some%20good%20quality%20meat-mutton%20tonight%2C%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20I%20should%20even%20be%20seen%20at%20your%20restaurant%20anymore.%20Imagine%20a%20policeman%20and%20his%20guest%20eating%20at%20the%20same%20place%20as%20a%20local%20rowdy!%20Kyun%20bhai%2C%20Salman%20Romeo%2C%20you%20have%20also%20come%20to%20eat%3F%E2%80%9D%20He%20turned%20to%20look%20at%20Salman%20who%20was%20still%20standing%20at%20the%20threshold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahman%20miyan%20half%20rose%20in%20his%20chair%20in%20welcome%20and%20in%20panic%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20myself%20thrown%20him%20out%20just%20as%20you%20arrived%20Inspector%20saheb.%20Get%20out!%E2%80%9D%20he%20shouted%20in%20a%20rather%20undignified%20manner%20at%20Salman%2C%20and%20burst%20into%20another%20coughing%20fit.%20%E2%80%9CWhere%E2%80%99s%20Abrar%3F%20Tell%20him%20to%20light%20the%20ovens%20%E2%80%93%20make%20fresh%20rotis.%20Sit%2C%20sit%20Inspector%20saheb%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20gestured%20with%20both%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Awdhesh%20Rana%20belched%20loudly.%20Rahman%20miyan%2C%20who%20was%20watching%20anxiously%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20food%20suits%20you%2C%20Inspector%20saheb%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstable%20Rana%20looked%20at%20his%20plate%20thoughtfully%20and%20said%20without%20malice%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20roti%20could%20have%20been%20a%20little%20more%20crisp%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20Rahman%20miyan%20turned%20towards%20the%20kitchen%20and%20shouted%20in%20his%20deep%20voice%2C%20%E2%80%9CAbrar!%20Did%20you%20hear%20that%3F%20You%E2%80%99re%20serving%20uncooked%20roti%20to%20Inspector%20sahib%20now%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20he%20looked%20towards%20Arshad%20and%20said%20gruffly%2C%20%E2%80%9CBring%20some%20fresh%20rotis.%20And%20make%20it%20crisp%20this%20time.%E2%80%9D%20Arshad%20lunged%20forward%20with%20a%20freshly%20baked%20tandoori%20roti%20in%20his%20hand%20and%20put%20it%20on%20their%20table.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CAnd%20get%20more%20gosht!%20What%20will%20sahib%20eat%20the%20roti%20with%3F%20Kanwal%20ji%20what%20will%20you%20take%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanwal%20leaned%20back%20in%20his%20chair%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20dal%3F%20You%20should%20learn%20how%20to%20make%20good%20dal.%E2%80%9D%20Rahman%20miyan%20nodded%20in%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20time%2C%20Constable%20Rana%20held%20up%20his%20palms%20to%20indicate%20that%20he%20had%20had%20enough.%20Then%20he%20patted%20the%20seat%20next%20to%20him%20and%20said%20softly%2C%20%E2%80%9CSit%2C%20Rahman%20ji%2C%20sit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahman%20miyan%20slipped%20onto%20the%20bench%20across%20the%20table%20and%20coughed%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20should%20have%20some%20kantheeka.%20It%20is%20very%20good%20for%20coughs%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kanwal.%20Rahman%20miyan%20had%20turned%20red%20and%20teary%20eyed%20from%20the%20coughing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToo%20much%20smoke%20from%20too%20much%20barbecue%2C%E2%80%9D%20Constable%20Rana%20said%20almost%20to%20himself%2C%20and%20then%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CKanwal%20ji%20here%20has%20started%20a%20youth%20group.%20He%20wants%20to%20inculcate%20dharma%20and%20good%20values%20in%20everyone.%20He%20has%20been%20telling%20me%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20illegal%20business%20going%20on%20in%20these%20galis.%20For%20instance%20I%20am%20getting%20constant%20complaints%20about%20Laadley%E2%80%99s%20meat%20business%2C%20haan%3F%20He%20is%20not%20caring%20about%20sentiments%20of%20people.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSaheb%2C%20what%20is%20wrong%20with%20serving%20nehari-kabab%3F%20His%20people%20have%