ation%20will%20do%20one%20thing%3B%20you%20will%20do%20the%20exact%20opposite.%20You%20allow%20people%20with%20jihadi%20tendencies%20into%20your%20restaurant.%20Madarsa%20jihadis%2C%20love%20jihadis%2C%20then%20supplying%20biryani%20to%20protestors%E2%80%A6%20It%20is%20becoming%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20answer%20my%20superiors.%20They%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98You%20are%20trying%20to%20protect%20Rahman%20miyan.%E2%80%99%20And%20really%2C%20the%20so-called%20information%20that%20you%20supply%20is%20useless.%20Some%20times%20I%20feel%20you%20get%20it%20from%20your%20colony%20WhatsApp%20group.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahman%20miyan%20and%20Arshad%20both%20looked%20at%20their%20feet%20for%20a%20few%20seconds.%20Then%20the%20silence%20was%20broken%20when%20Rana%20made%20a%20show%20of%20taking%20out%20his%20purse%2C%20and%20Rahman%20miyan%20snapped%20back%20into%20the%20present%20and%20remembered%20his%20manners.%20%E2%80%9CSaheb%2C%20what%20are%20you%20doing%3F%20You%20are%20our%20honourable%20guest.%20Eh%2C%20pack%20some%20kabab%20for%20saheb%E2%80%99s%20Mrs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20what%20are%20you%20saying!%20My%20wife%20is%20not%20communist%20like%20Achche%20bhai%E2%80%99s%20Mrs.%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20constable%20tittered.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20sanatani.%20She%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20it%20in%20the%20house.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20morning%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAamna%20barged%20into%20the%20room.%20%E2%80%9CJamal%2C%20wake%20up!%20Rahman%20miyan%20is%20dead.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%3F%20I%20just%20saw%20him%20last%20evening.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYour%20Abba%20has%20left%20already.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20taken%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20body%20for%20post%20mortem%20and%20are%20not%20releasing%20it.%20Somebody%20had%20to%20go%20to%20see%20how%20soon%20they%20would%20return%20the%20body%2C%20so%20your%20Abba%20has%20gone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%