20forehead%20had%20a%20deep%20gash%20and%20was%20pressed%20against%20the%20steam%20iron%2C%20which%20was%20also%20lying%20on%20the%20floor.%20Haji%20saheb%20had%20turned%20black.%20There%20was%20so%20much%20blood%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arshad%20shivered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSomebody%20has%20stolen%20the%20gosht%20ka%20pateela%20from%20the%20kitchen%2C%20with%20all%20the%20paaya%20in%20it.%20Other%20pateelas%20are%20also%20missing.%20Haji%20saheb%E2%80%99s%20aluminium%20tiffin%20carrier%20is%20gone%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Abrar%20quietly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20robbery%20inside%20also.%20His%20counter%20has%20been%20toppled%20over%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Arshad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaadley%20put%20his%20hands%20on%20Arshad%E2%80%99s%20shoulders%2C%20ostensibly%20in%20order%20to%20comfort%20him%2C%20but%20it%20only%20made%20Arshad%20lose%20his%20balance%20and%20stumble%20slightly.%20%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20he%20will%20faint%20from%20the%20sadma%2C%E2%80%9D%20shouted%20Salman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20be%20melodramatic%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abrar%20snapped%20back.%20At%20that%20moment%2C%20Arshad%20and%20Abrar%20were%20both%20summoned%20inside%20by%20begum%20saheba%20to%20receive%20instructions%20regarding%20the%20funeral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20there%20last%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jamal%20glancing%20towards%20Habib.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20a%20long%20conversation%20with%20him%2C%20no%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20after%20everyone%20left%2C%20Awdhesh%20Rana%20and%20Kanwal%20came%20to%20the%20restaurant%20and%20even%20threatened%20haji%20saheb.%20I%20was%20there%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20but%20they%20made%20me%20leave%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Salman%20conspiratorially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKanwal%20was%20there%20too%3F%20What%20was%20that%20scoundrel%20doing%20in%20our%20gali%3F%E2%80%9D%20Laadley%20spat%20on%20the%20ground.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20we%20know%20who%20is%20responsible%20for%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20Asghar%2C%20returned%20with%20Balabhadra%20babu%20to%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20where%20the%20whole%20mohalla%20was%20gathered.%20Both%20declared%20that%20they%20had%20%E2%80%98spoken%20to%20people%E2%80%99%20and%20that%20the%20body%20would%20be%20returned%20by%20Asr%20time%20for%20burial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20spoken%20to%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20Balabhadra%20babu%20said%20confidently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20requested%20Achche%20to%20intervene%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Asghar%20supportively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20also%20tried%20helpfully%20to%20answer%20people%E2%80%99s%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20no%20Beta%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20his%20head%20was%20smashed%20with%20the%20steam%20iron%20or%20whether%20he%20fell%20on%20top%20of%20it.%20Post%20mortem%20results%20are%20awaited%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Balabhadra%20babu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20injury%20to%20the%20head%20could%20be%20ante-mortem.%20The%20concerned%20person%20said%20that%20the%20body%20was%20blue%20and%20it%20seemed%20he%20had%20choked%20on%20something%20%E2%80%93%20it%20could%20be%20an%20asthma%20attack%20even%2C%E2%80%9D%20Asghar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20mean%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20murder%3F%20But%20there%20has%20been%20a%20robbery%20too.%20Abrar%20is%20saying%20that%20the%20gosht%20ka%20pateela%20is%20gone%2C%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Habib.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20it%20has%20to%20be%20a%20Mohammadan%20who%20has%20done%20it!%20We%20won%E2%80%99t%20kill%20for%20gosht%20ka%20pateela%2C%E2%80%9D%20blurted%20Shambhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalabhadra%20babu%20gave%20him%20an%20annoyed%20look%2C%20and%20then%20changed%20the%20subject.%20%E2%80%9CArre%20Abrar%2C%20why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20serve%20some%20biscuits%3F%20Body%20will%20still%20take%20some%20hours.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20afternoon%2C%20the%20men