ng%20well%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchumacher's%20lawyer%2C%20Felix%20Damm%2C%20however%2C%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20former%20F1%20driver's%20family%20has%20decided%20not%20to%20make%20his%20final%20health%20report%20public%20due%20to%20privacy%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20always%20about%20protecting%20private%20things.%20We%20considered%20whether%20a%20final%20report%20about%20Michael's%20health%20could%20be%20the%20right%20way%20to%20do%20this%2C%3A%20Damm%20told%20German%20media%20outlet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lto.de%2Frecht%2Fhintergruende%2Fh%2Ffelix-damm-interview-michael-schumacher-unfall-2013-2023%2F%5C%22%3ELTO%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.si.com%2Ffannation%2Fracing%2Ff1briefings%2Fnews%2Ff1-news-michael-schumachers-lawyer-reveals-real-reason-for-secrecy-behind-final-medical-report-sj4%5C%22%3ESI.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDamm%20also%20stated%20that%20Schumacher's%20family%20would%20have%20come%20under%20pressure%20from%20the%20media%20to%20release%20timely%20health%20updates%2C%20had%20they%20released%20the%20final%20health%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20that%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20the%20end%20of%20it%20and%20there%20would%20have%20had%20to%20be%20constantly%20updated%20'water%20level%20reports'%20and%20it%20would%20not%20have%20been%20up%20to%20the%20family%20when%20the%20media%20interest%20in%20the%20story%20stopped.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20%5Bthe%20media%5D%20could%20pick%20up%20on%20such%20a%20report%20again%20and%20again%20and%20as%20'and%20what%20does%20it%20look%20like%20now%3F'%20one%2C%20two%2C%20three%20months%20or%20years%20after%20the%20message%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20then%20wanted%20to%20take%20action%20against%20this%20reporting%2C%20we%20would%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20argument%20of%20voluntary%20self-disclosure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20report%20in%20German%20outlet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bild.de%2Fbild-plus%2Fsport%2Fmotorsport%2Fmotorsport%2Fformel-1-schumachers-ski-unfall-vor-10-jahren-boxenfunk-sollte-ihm-bei-der-reha-86545232.bild.html%5C%22%3EBILD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Schumacher%20has%20been%20driven%20in%20a%20Mercedes%20AMG%20car%20to%20stimulate%20the%20brain%20with%20familiar%20sounds.%20This%20was%20done%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20because%20the%20racing%20great%20spent%20over%20two%20decades%20in%20Formula%20One%20or%20in%20other%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20adds%20that%20Michael%20Schumacher%20receives%2024-hour%20care%2C%20with%20a%20private%20infirmary%20situated%20in%20his%20former%20office.%2015%20doctors%20and%20their%20assistants%20ensure%20his%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchumacher%20won%20seven%20F1%20world%20titles%2C%20including%20five%20on%20a%20trot%20with%20Ferrari.%20He%20returned%20to%20the%20F1%20racing%20in%202010%20for%20three%20years%20with%20the%20Mercedes%20team.%20He%20was%20replaced%20by%20Lewis%20Hamilton%20in%202013.%20In%202021%2C%20Hamilton%20matched%20Schumacher's%20record%20of%20seven%20world%20titles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20AFP%20Inputs)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704009300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-12%2Fgou9avn_michael-schumacher-afp_625x300_17_December_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fformula-1%2Ffinal-report-about-michael-schumachers-health-f1-greats-lawyer-reveals-new-details-4774346%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It's%20been%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20since%20Formula%201%20legend%20Michael%20Schumacher%20suffered%20a%20life-threatening%20injury%20while%20skiing%20in%20the%20French%20ski%20resort%20of%20Meribel%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fformula-1%2Ffinal-report-about-michael-schumachers-health-f1-greats-lawyer-reveals-new-details-4774346%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fformula-1%2Ffinal-report-about-michael-schumachers-health-f1-greats-lawyer-reveals-new-details-4774346%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fformula-1%2Ffinal-report-about-michael-schumachers-health-f1-greats-lawyer-reveals-new-details-4774346%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20Teen%20Shoots%20Dead%20Sister%20After%20Fight%20Over%20Filming%20TikTok%20Video%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20tragic%20incident%2C%20a%2014-year-old%20girl%20fatally%20shot%20her%20sister%20during%20a%20dispute%20over%20a%20TikTok%20video%20in%20Sarai%20Alamgir%20town%2C%20located%20in%20Punjab's%20Gujrat%20district%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20ARY%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20details%2C%20a%20quarrel%20erupted%20between%20the%20two%20sisters%2C%20Saba%20Afzal%20and%20Maria%20Afzal%2C%20while%20they%20were%20filming%20a%20video%20for%20the%20popular%20social%20media%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20intense%20argument%2C%20the%2014-year-old%2C%20Saba%20Afzal%2C%20took%20a%20drastic%20step%20by%20shooting%20her%20sister.%20A%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20the%20young%20suspect%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20lodged%20by%20her%20brother%20with%20the%20Saddar%20Police%20Station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20distressing%20incident%20echoes%20a%20similar%20tragedy%20from%20December%2C%20where%20three%20youths%20lost%20their%20lives%20while%20engaged%20in%20filming%20a%20video%20for%20TikTok%20near%20Sheikhupura%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unfortunate%20victims%2C%20residents%20of%20Khanqah%20Dogran%20city%20in%20Safdarabad%20Tehsil%2C%20were%20on%20a%20motorcycle%20recording%20a%20TikTok%20video.%20Unfortunately%2C%20due%20to%20distraction%2C%20their%20motorcycle%20collided%20head-on%20with%20a%20car%20approaching%20from%20the%20opposite%20direction%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20tragic%20demise%20of%20all%20three%20youngsters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20on%20December%2024%2C%20Jamia%20Binoria%20Town%2C%20a%20prominent%20religious%20school%20in%20Karachi%2C%20the%20capital%20of%20Sindh%20province%2C%20issued%20a%20fatwa%20(a%20religious%20decree)%20declaring%20the%20use%20of%20TikTok%20illegal%20and%20'haram'%2C%20terming%20it%20the%20biggest%20temptation%20of%20the%20modern%20era%2C%20Pakistani%20vernacular%20media%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fatwa%2C%20the%20institution%20outlined%20ten%20reasons%20supporting%20its%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fatwa%2C%20delivered%20online%20by%20Jamia%20Binoria%2C%20asserts%20that%20TikTok%20poses%20an%20increasing%20danger%20as%20a%20'fitna'%20(temptation)%20in%20the%20present%20age%20and%20is%20considered%20illegal%20and%20haram%20from%20a%20Shariah%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20reasons%20cited%2C%20the%20app's%20inclusion%20of%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20animals%20is%20deemed%20forbidden%20in%20Sharia%2C%20and%20the%20creation%20and%20dissemination%20of%20obscene%20videos%20by%20women%20on%20the%20platform%20is%20highlighted%2C%20Dawn%20News%20TV%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20fatwa%20condemns%20the%20practice%20of%20men%20and%20women%20on%20TikTok%20making%20videos%20involving%20dancing%20and%20singing%2C%20which%20is%20viewed%20as%20a%20means%20of%20spreading%20obscenity%20and%20nudity%2C%20deemed%20a%20waste%20of%20time%20and%20leading%20to%20moral%20decay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamia%20Banoria's%20fatwa%20underscores%20that%20TikTok%20not%20only%20contains%20videos%20that%20mock%20scholars%20and%20religion%20but%20is%20a%20platform%20where%20everything%20can%20be%20subjected%20to%20mockery%20and%20ridicule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20religious%20scholars%20have%20been%20calling%20for%20a%20ban%20on%20TikTok%20as%20a%20reason%20for%20spreading%20immorality%2C%20and%20a%20partial%20ban%20has%20also%20been%20imposed%20on%20TikTok%20time%20and%20again%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Dawn%20News%20TV%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20Telecommunication%20Authority%20imposed%20a%20five-month%20ban%20on%20the%20video-sharing%20app%20from%20July%20to%20November.%20The%20ban%20was%20lifted%20after%20TikTok%20provided%20assurances%20that%20it%20would%20enhance%20measures%20to%20control%20indecent%20or%20immoral%20content%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20The%20Express%20Tribune%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704009240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-09%2Ft9loafp_tiktok-reuters_625x300_20_September_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpak-teen-shoots-dead-sister-after-fight-over-filming-tiktok-video-4774306%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20tragic%20incident%2C%20a%2014-year-old%20girl%20fatally%20shot%20her%20sister%20during%20a%20dispute%20over%20a%20TikTok%20video%20in%20Sarai%20Alamgir%20town%2C%20located%20in%20Punjab's%20Gujrat%20district%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20ARY%20News.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpak-teen-shoots-dead-sister-after-fight-over-filming-tiktok-video-4774306%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpak-teen-shoots-dead-sister-after-fight-over-filming-tiktok-video-4774306%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpak-teen-shoots-dead-sister-after-fight-over-filming-tiktok-video-4774306%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ajay%20wraps%202023%20with%20UNSEEN%20pictures%20with%20family%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704009027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto