Soup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOffice%20of%20the%20Historian%3C%2Fa%3E%20website%2C%20which%20reads%3A%20%26quot%3BBean%20soup%20became%20a%20permanent%20fixture%20in%20the%20institution%20when%20Speaker%20Joe%20Cannon%20of%20Illinois%20discovered%20that%20his%20favorite%20meal%20had%20not%20been%20prepared%20by%20the%20kitchen%20staff%20on%20a%20hot%2C%20summer%20day%20in%201904.%20Dismayed%20by%20the%20omission%2C%20the%20Speaker%20directed%20that%20bean%20soup%20be%20served%20in%20the%20House%20every%20day%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20weather.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recipe's%20bare-bones%20ingredient%20list%20includes%20navy%20beans%2C%20ham%20hocks%2C%20onion%2C%20and%20butter.%20Dubois'%20variation%20of%20the%20soup%2C%20which%20is%20recorded%20on%20the%20Senate%20site%2C%20contains%20celery%2C%20parsley%2C%20garlic%2C%20and%20a%20quart%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftrying-best-mashed-potato-recipes-from-chefs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emashed%20potatoes%3C%2Fa%3E%20(yes%2C%20really).%20Both%20Senate%20versions%20are%20boiled%20in%20water%2C%20not%20stock%2C%20and%20Dubois'%20modifications%20exclude%20seasoning%20of%20any%20kind%2C%20while%20the%20base%20recipe%20includes%20salt%20and%20pepper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20House%20version%2C%20a%20slight%20variation%20on%20the%20famous%20Senate%20restaurant%20bean%20soup%20recipe%20published%20in%20a%201955%20House%20restaurant%20menu%2C%20calls%20for%20Michigan%20beans%20and%20omits%20the%20onion%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20pepper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20nary%20a%20bay%20leaf%20in%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20soup%20boasts%20over%20a%20century%20of%20historical%20significance%2C%20with%20the%20kitchen%20omitting%20the%20dish%20from%20the%20menu%20on%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwamu.org%2Fstory%2F14%2F12%2F12%2Fsteeped_in_tradition_the_story_of_the_senates_signature_soup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20recorded%20day%20during%20WWII%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%20tradition%20began%2C%20the%20basic%20soup%20is%20a%20simple%20but%20powerful%20example%20of%20the%20much-needed%20upgrades%20and%20new%20flavors%20needed%20in%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20humble%20hero%20that%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-rachael-ray-emeril-lagasse-chicken-noodle-soup-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20good%20soup%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20even%20pantry-clearing%20meals%20on%20a%20budget%20need%20not%20be%20so%20bland.%20Consider%20the%20depth%20of%20flavor%20one%20can%20achieve%20merely%20by%20substituting%20stock%20for%20the%20water%20or%20adding%20a%20single%20herb.%20As%20much%20as%20this%20recipe%20could%20be%20transformed%20into%20a%20nourishing%2C%20delicious%20meal%20with%20just%20a%20few%20small%20changes%2C%20Congress%20would%20also%20benefit%20immensely%20from%20a%20little%20variation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Congress%20remains%20less%20diverse%20than%20the%20US%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20with%20non-Hispanic%20white%20Americans%20representing%2075%25%20of%20voting%20members%2C%20according%20to%20statistics%20maintained%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pewresearch.org%2Fshort-reads%2F2023%2F02%2F07%2Fthe-changing-face-of-congress%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPew%20Research%20Center%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20female%20representation%20in%20Congress%20is%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%2C%20women%20comprise%20just%2028%25%20of%20all%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2013%20publicly%20out%20LGBTQ%2B%20Congresspeople%20make%20up%20just%202%25%20of%20the%20House%20and%20Senate%2C%20compared%20to%206.5%25%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20a%202020%20report%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.opensecrets.org%2Fnews%2F2020%2F04%2Fmajority-of-lawmakers-millionaires%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenSecrets%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%20half%20of%20Congress%20are%20millionaires.%20And%2C%20on%20average%2C%20members%20of%20Congress%20are%2020%20years%20older%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20our%20elected%20representatives%20don't%20feel%20like%20they%20represent%20the%20average%20American%20because%20most%20congressional%20members%20don't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20it's%20no%20wonder%20they're%20so%20out%20of%20touch%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0they're%20stuck%20in%20a%20timewarp%20where%20four-ingredient%20bean%20soup%20without%20salt%20is%20a%20delicacy%20worthy%20of%20eating%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbasic-bean-soup-served-every-day-congress-120-years-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704008077000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65910311ec62ab5daf7fcc56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbasic-bean-soup-served-every-day-congress-120-years-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20simple%20bean%20soup%20with%20just%20four%20ingredients%20has%20been%20served%20every%20day%20to%20members%20of%20Congress%20for%20over%20a%20century.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbasic-bean-soup-served-every-day-congress-120-years-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20war%3A%20Russia%20hits%20back%20after%20Kyiv%20attack%20on%20border%20city%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704007931000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F7839%2Fproduction%2F_132177703_mediaitem132177702.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67851431%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20latest%20attacks%20on%20Kyiv