%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DA%2520British%2520passenger%2520has%2520died%2CAirport%2520at%25205.30pm%2520yesterday.%5C%22%3EMetro%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20the%20female%20traveler%20was%20on%20TUI%20flight%20BY1573%2C%20which%20departed%20Tenerife%20Sur%20Airport%20around%205%3A30%20PM%20local%20time.%20However%2C%20she%20suffered%20a%20cardiac%20arrest%20shortly%20after%20take-off.%C2%A0Almost%20an%20hour%20into%20the%20flight%2C%20crews%20issued%20an%20emergency%20Squawk%207700%20signal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Glasgow-bound%20flight%20was%20then%20diverted%20to%20Funchal%20Airport%20on%20the%20island%20of%20Madeira%20at%20around%206.20%20pm.%20Approximately%2020%20minutes%20after%20the%20emergency%20signal%2C%20the%20plane%20touched%20down%20on%20the%20Portuguese%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20woman%20could%20not%20be%20saved%20despite%20the%20efforts%20of%20medical%20and%20emergency%20crews%20on%20the%20ground.%20Her%20identity%20has%20not%20been%20revealed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20delay%20of%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20the%20flight%20resumed%C2%A0its%20journey%C2%A0en%20route%20to%20Glasgow%20at%208%3A55%20pm%20last%20night.%20The%20airline%20has%20not%20yet%20released%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20tragedy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20back%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpilot-dies-in-bathroom-on-miami-flight-forcing-emergency-landing-4304587%5C%22%3Epilot%20died%20after%20collapsing%20in%20the%20bathroom%20of%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20commercial%20flight%20from%20Miami%20to%20Chile%20with%20271%20passengers%20on%20board.%C2%A0The%20incident%20prompted%20an%20emergency%20landing%20in%20Panama%2C%20which%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20co-pilot.%C2%A0Captain%20Ivan%20Andaur%2C%20the%20pilot%20who%20died%2C%20began%20feeling%20unwell%20three%20hours%20after%20the%20LATAM%20Airlines%20flight%20took%20off.%20He%20was%20given%20emergency%20treatment%20by%20the%20crew%2C%20b