Olympic%20Games%20in%207%20months%20but%20no%20one%20seems%20serious%20about%20it%20while%20in%20the%20last%20four%20Olympics%2C%20wrestlers%20brought%20consecutive%20medals%2C%E2%80%9D%20Punia%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704005072000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F31120945%2FScreenshot-2023-12-31-at-12.09.08-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwrestler-vinesh-phogat-leaves-khel-ratna-arjuna-awards-on-kartavya-path-in-protest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20said%20that%20such%20awards%20were%20meaningless%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20women%20wrestlers%20were%20struggling%20to%20get%20justice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwrestler-vinesh-phogat-leaves-khel-ratna-arjuna-awards-on-kartavya-path-in-protest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3B25-30%20Crore%20Khaate%20Mein%26quot%3B%3A%20Harbhajan's%20Hilarious%20Meme%20On%20Starc's%20IPL%20Deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mitchell%20Starc%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1416-mitchell-starc-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMitchell%20Starc%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Australia's%20World%20Cup-winning%20pacer%2C%20became%20the%20most%20expensive%20player%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%2C%20after%20he%20was%20bought%20for%20Rs%2024.75%20crore%20by%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20at%20the%20Players%20Auction%20earlier%20this%20month.%20Starc%20became%20the%20second%20player%20to%20breach%20the%20Rs%2020%20crore%20mark%20during%20the%20IPL%202024%20auction%2C%20following%20SunRisers%20Hyderabad's%20Rs%2020.5%20crore%20bid%20for%20Australia%20captain%20and%20star%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pat%20Cummins%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1656-pat-cummins-playerprofile%5