lm%20are%20when%20he%20argues%20in%20court%20against%20senior%20lawyers%20%E2%80%93%20in%20real-life%20Ram%20Jethmalani%2C%20Salman%20Khurshid%20and%20Subramaniam%20Swamy%20%E2%80%93%20hired%20by%20the%20godman.%20Bajpayee%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20combines%20in%20these%20moments%20fanboy%20awe%20and%20veneration%20for%20these%20legendary%20seniors%20with%20a%20brave%20and%20robust%20commitment%20to%20his%20calling%20and%20the%20righteousness%20of%20his%20cause.%20He%20is%20empathetic%20and%20supportive%20to%20the%20girl%2C%20and%20he%20does%20not%20flinch%20even%20after%20a%20series%20of%20key%20witnesses%20are%20murdered%20and%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20his%20life%20is%20in%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIdealism%20is%20what%20also%20sustains%20the%20central%20protagonist%20in%20Vidhu%20Vinod%20Chopra%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3E12th%C2%A0Fail%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eanother%20exhilarating%20real-life%20story%20of%20a%20young%20man%20from%20a%20remote%20village%20in%20the%20Chambal%20region%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(Manoj%20Kumar%20Sharma)%20who%20fights%20incredible%20odds%20to%20qualify%20finally%20in%20the%20most%20fiercely%20contested%20competitive%20examination%20in%20the%20country%20to%20become%20an%20IPS%20officer.%20As%20a%20young%20man%20he%20meets%20a%20police%20officer%20who%20is%20honest%2C%20kind%20and%20just.%20This%20encounter%20alters%20the%20course%20of%20his%20life.%20It%20is%20the%20dream%20to%20become%20a%20police%20officer%20like%20him%20that%20drives%20him%20to%20the%20city%2C%20where%20he%20survives%20through%20years%20of%20hard%20manual%20labour%2C%20disappointments%20and%20setbacks%20to%20study%20for%20the%20examination.%20He%20persists%20to%20rise%20again%20and%20again%20against%20defeat%20and%20hardship%2C%20to%20finally%20overcome.%20Vikram%20Massey%20brings%20a%20rare%20sensitivity%20and%20authenticity%20to%20his%20portrayal%2C%20raising%20him%20to%20the%20top%20rung%20of%20our%20actors.%20It%20is%20hard%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20to%20forget%20the%20sequenc