on's%20embodiment%20of%20the%20'Viksit%20Bharat'%20(developed%20India)%20spirit%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20importance%20of%20sustaining%20this%20momentum%20into%202024.%20The%20broadcast%20also%20featured%20a%20segment%20on%20physical%20and%20mental%20well-being%20as%20part%20of%20the%20'Fit%20India'%20initiative%2C%20with%20contributions%20from%20Sadhguru%2C%20Harmanpreet%20Kaur%2C%20Vishwanathan%20Anand%2C%20and%20Akshay%20Kumar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmann-ki-baat-pm-modi-highlights-viksit-bharat-physical-mental-health-ai-tool-space-missions-sports-achievements-and-others-in-last-episode-of-2023%2Farticleshow%2F106415887.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Census%20Till%20At%20Least%20October%202024%2C%20Ninth%20Extension%20of%20Deadline%3A%20The%20Hindu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F07202552%2FScreenshot-2022-02-07-at-8.25.47-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Additional%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%20(RGI)%20has%20informed%20the%20states%20on%20December%2030%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fwith-announcement-of-new-notification-census-to-be-delayed-till-at-least-october-2024%2Farticle67690661.ece%5C%22%3Ereports%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20the%20competent%20authority%20has%20decided%20to%20further%20extend%20the%20date%20of%20freezing%20of%20administrative%20boundaries%20up%20to%20June%2030%2C%202024.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20rules%20out%20the%20Census%20exercise%20before%20the%202024%20general%20election%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20held%20in%20April%20and%20May%20next%20year.%20This%20is%20the%20ninth%20such%20extension%20of%20the%20deadline%2C%E2%80%9D%20writes%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extension%20of%20this%20deadline%20to%20freeze%20the%20administrative%20boundaries%20of%20districts%2C%20tehsils%2C%20towns%20and%20municipal%20bodies%20impacts%20the%20already%20delayed%20census%2C%20as%20it%20%E2%80%9Cusually%20takes%20about%20three%20months%20after%20the%20boundaries%20are%20set%20to%20identify%20and%20train%20the%20enumerators%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20implications%20on%20a%20variety%20of%20programmes%20and%20estimations%20that%20the%20government%20and%20others%20make%20over%20needs%20of%20the%20population%2C%20as%20the%20Census%20is%20the%20largest%20public%20body%20of%20data%20about%20the%20country%20available%20and%20updated.%20It%20may%20even%20render%20those%20seen%20as%20needing%20extra%20care%20under%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%20among%20the%20uncounted%20and%20therefore%20not%20helped%20by%20government%20schemes.%20The%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20passed%20in%20the%20special%20session%20of%20parliament%20is%20contingent%20on%20the%20next%20delimitation%2C%20which%20depends%20on%20the%20next%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20latest%20decision%20of%20the%20Addl.%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%20regarding%20the%20freezing%20of%20administrative%20boundaries%20until%20October%202024%20is%20perplexing%20as%20no%20reasons%20have%20been%20publicised%20for%20the%20same.%20We%2C%20the%20citizenry%20are%20completely%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20the%20plans%20for%20conducting%20the%20long%20overdue%20decennial%20census.%202023%20was%20a%20largely%20Covid%20infection%20free%20year%20but%20census%20data%20collection%20exercise%20was%20not%20initiated.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20up-to-date%20data%2C%20how%20will%20the%20State%20and%20Central%20governments%20plan%20developmental%20programmes%20and%20poverty%20eradication%20schemes%20is%20a%20billion%20dollar%20question.%20The%20non-disclosure%20of%20certain%20annual%20reports%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%20in%20light%20of%20the%20trend%20that%20has%20emerged%20over%20recent%20years%20of%20stalling%20the%20publication%20of%20crucial%20demographic%20and%20economic%20statistics%20giving%20some%20technical%20excuse%20or%20the%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20transparency%20rights%20activist%20Venkatesh%20Nayak%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20Census%2C%20the%20office%20of%20the%20RGI%20and%20the%20Census%20Commissioner%20of%20India%20have%20also%20not%20released%20two%20important%20reports%20on%20the%20registration%20of%20births%2C%20deaths%2C%20and%20causes%20of%20deaths%20for%20the%20years%202021%2C%202022%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20writes%20that%20the%20report%20on%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcensusindia.gov.in%2Fnada%2Findex.php%2Fcatalog%2F42542%5C%22%3EVital%20Statistics%20of%20India%20Based%20On%20The%20Civil%20Registration%20System%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20for%202020%20was%20only%20released%20in%20May%202022.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20vital%20statistics%20are%20invaluable%20for%20planning%2C%C2%A0monitoring%20and%20evaluating%20various%20programmes%20related%20to%20primary%20health%20care%2C%20family%20planning%2C%C2%A0maternal%20and%20child%20health%2C%20education%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20cites%20the%20report%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20annual%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcensusindia.gov.in%2Fnada%2Findex.php%2Fcatalog%2F42681%2Fdownload%2F46350%2FAnnual_Report_on_MCCD_2020.pdf%5C%22%3EReport%20On%20Medical%20Certification%20Of%20Cause%20of%20Death%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20was%20last%20released%20for%20the%20year%202020.%20This%20report%20carries%20statistics%20on%20the%20causes%20of%20deaths%2C%20cross-tabulating%20them%20by%20age%20and%20sex%20of%20the%20deceased.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20wide%20divergence%2C%20almost%20ten-fold%2C%20between%20India%E2%80%99s%20reported%20figures%20on%20COVID-19%20and%20that%20estimated%20globally%20by%20the%20WHO.%20The%20official%20document%20would%20bring%20more%20clarity%20on%20this%20but%20it%20remains%20unreleased.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704004202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F07202552%2FScreenshot-2022-02-07-at-8.25.47-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-census-till-at-least-october-2024-ninth-extension-of-deadline-the-hindu%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%222021%20was%20the%20first%20time%20the%20decennial%20census%20of%20India%20was%20postponed%20in%20150%20years.%20No%20report%20on%20births%2C%20deaths%20and%20causes%20of%20deaths%20has%20also%20been%20released%20by%20the%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%20for%202021%2C%202022%20and%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-census-till-at-least-october-2024-ninth-extension-of-deadline-the-hindu%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Please%20don't%20bother%20Jeff%20Bezos%20on%20vacation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20large%20sailing%20yacht%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659108a1ec62ab5daf7fcc70%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeff%20Bezos's%20megayacht%20%26quot%3BKoru%26quot%3B%20is%20seen%20docked%20at%20Port%20Everglades%20in%20Port%20Everglades%2C%20Florida.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Raedle%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJeff%20Bezos%20has%20been%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20on%20his%20%24500%20million%20mega-yacht%2C%20Koru.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKoru%20recently%20made%20a%20stop%20at%20Antigua%20in%20the%20Caribbean.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELocal%20officials%20have%20asked%20the%20public%20to%20give%20the%20billionaire%20some%20privacy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJeff%20Bezos'%20%24500%20million%20megayacht%20is%20such%20a%20spectacle%20to%20behold%20that%20local%20