practice%20Tests%20would%20have%20given%20the%20team%20any%20benefit%20because%20of%20the%20'contrasting%20difference'%20in%20the%20two%20situations.%20After%20India%20lost%20the%20opening%20Test%20to%20South%20Africa%20by%20an%20innings%20and%2032%20runs%2C%20Rohit%20was%20asked%20in%20the%20press%20conference%20about%20the%20team's%20decision%20to%20snub%20practice%20matches%20over%20intra-squad%20contests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20highlighted%20the%20nature%20of%20wickets%20and%20the%20opponent%20team's%20players%20in%20the%20practice%20matches%20as%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20team's%20decision%20to%20play%20intra-squad%20matches%20instead.%20The%20India%20skipper%20claimed%20that%20the%20wickets%20the%20team%20gets%20in%20practice%20matches%20don't%20produce%20the%20sort%20of%20bounce%20and%20pace%20the%20actual%20match%20pitches%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20playing%20practice%20matches%20in%20the%20last%204-5%20years.%20We%20also%20tried%20to%20play%20first-class%20matches.%20The%20wicket%20that%20you%20get%20in%20the%20matches%2C%20you%20won't%20get%20that%20in%20the%20practice%20matches.%20It%20is%20better%20that%20we%20prepare%20according%20to%20our%20requirements%2C%20we%20prepare%20the%20pitch%20according%20to%20our%20requirements.%20We%20can%20have%20control%20of%20the%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohit%20in%20a%20media%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20went%20to%20Australia%20the%20last%20time%2C%20when%20we%20played%20in%20South%20Africa%20in%202018%2C%20the%20ball%20didn't%20bounce%20beyond%20the%20knee-roll%20on%20practice%20pitches.%20But%20here%2C%20the%20ball%20flies%20over%20your%20head.%20So%2C%20all%20these%20things%20were%20considered%20and%20we%20decided%20to%20prepare%20according%20to%20our%20own%20style%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20said%20he%20is%20open%20to%20playing%20practice%20Tests%20on%20tours%2C%20provided%20the%20wickets%20offered%20a%20similar%20to%20the%20ones%20that%20are%20used%20in%20actual%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20get%20the%20conditions%20in%20a%20practice%20match%20that%20would%20be%20similar%20to%20the%20ones%20in%20the%20Tests%2C%20then%20it's%20fine.%20Bowlers%20also%2C%20we%20get%20pacers%20who%20bowl%20120-125%20kph.%20We%20have%20experienced%20that%20in%20the%20last%20two%20or%20three%20practice%20matches.%20It's%20better%20we%20face%20our%20own%20bowlers%20and%20prepare%20pitch%20according%20to%20our%20will%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704000120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F3bfsdsp8_rohit-pc_625x300_29_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fwhy-team-india-doesnt-play-first-class-practice-matches-rohit-sharmas-honest-answers-4762460%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rohit%20Sharma%20explained%20the%20reason%20behind%20Team%20India's%20reluctance%20to%20play%20First%20Class%20practice%20Tests%20on%20overseas%20tours.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fwhy-team-india-doesnt-play-first-class-practice-matches-rohit-sharmas-honest-answers-4762460%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fwhy-team-india-doesnt-play-first-class-practice-matches-rohit-sharmas-honest-answers-4762460%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fsouth-africa-vs-india-2023-24%2Fwhy-team-india-doesnt-play-first-class-practice-matches-rohit-sharmas-honest-answers-4762460%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hoteliers%20cash%20in%20on%20New%20Year%20festivities%2C%20no%20impact%20of%20Covid-19%20resurgence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704000003000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F202