-silicon-valley-debate-spotlight-2023-12%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHow%2520Sam%2520Altman%2527s%2520OpenAI%2520drama%2Can%2520e%252Facc%2520or%2520decel%253F%26amp%3Btext%3DDisagreements%2520over%2520the%2520speed%2520of%2Chow%2520to%2520approach%2520artificial%2520intelligence.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estaunchly%20pro-AI%20ideology%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20has%20Silicon%20Valley%20split%20over%20how%20artificial%20intelligence%20should%20be%20regulated%20%E2%80%94%20appears%20to%20be%20walking%20a%20razor's%20edge%20between%20being%20a%20techno-libertarian%20philosophy%20and%20a%20nihilistic%2C%20even%20reckless%2C%20approach%20to%20advancing%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20significant%20technological%20developments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20its%20public%20proponents%2C%20like%20Garry%20Tan%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20startup%20accelerator%20Y%20Combinator%20and%20former%20cofounder%20of%20the%20venture%20firm%20Initialized%20Capital%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgarrytan%2Fstatus%2F1682458510033047552%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Einsist%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20%26quot%3Be%2Facc%26quot%3B%20is%20not%20about%20replacing%20humans%20with%20robots%2C%20it's%20not%20exactly%20%3Cem%3Enot%20%3C%2Fem%3Eabout%20replacing%20humans%20with%20robots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20riff%20on%20the%20effective%20altruism%2C%20or%20%26quot%3BEA%2C%26quot%3B%20philosophy%20touted%20by%20tech%20influencers%20like%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feffective-altruism-how-started-how-its-going-after-ftx-collapse-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20e%2Facc%20took%20off%20in%202023%2C%20though%20its%20exact%20origins%20remain%20unclear.%20The%20movement%20has%20attracted%20a%20cast%20of%20unlikely%20characters%2C%20including%20venture%20capitalist%20Marc%20Andreessen%20and%20convicted%20fraudster%20Martin%20Shkreli.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEA%20and%20e%2Facc%20are%20mostly%20the%20same%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Emmett%20Shear%2C%20the%20former%20interim%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmeridian.mercury.com%2Femmett-shear-part-one%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeridian%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20only%20difference%20is%20a%20value%20judgment%20on%20whether%20or%20not%20humanity%20getting%20wiped%20out%20is%20a%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EE%2Faccs%20(pronounced%20ee-yacks)%20adherents%20believe%20the%20creation%20of%20an%20AI%20singularity%2C%20where%20technology%20advances%20beyond%20the%20point%20of%20human%20control%2C%20is%20not%20only%20unavoidable%20but%20desirable%20%E2%80%94%20a%20necessary%20part%20of%20evolution%20beyond%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20investing%20in%20getting%20there%20could%20mean%20big%20money%20as%20e%2Faccs%20spur%20increased%20controversy%20and%20interest%20in%20the%20AI%20industry%2C%20the%20development%20of%20which%20is%20driving%20such%20strong%20market%20changes%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goldmansachs.com%2Fintelligence%2Fpages%2Fgenerative-ai-could-raise-global-gdp-by-7-percent.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20estimates%20generative%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAI%20could%20increase%20the%20global%20GDP%20by%20%247%20trillion%2C%20or%207%25%2C%20over%20the%20next%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'No%20affinity%20for%20biological%20humans'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20jargon-filled%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feffectiveacceleration.tech%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cu%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20spreading%20the%20gospel%20of%20Effective%20Accelerationism%20describes%20%26quot%3Btechnocapitalistic%20progress%26quot%3B%20as%20inevitable%2C%20lauding%20e%2Facc%20proponents%20as%20builders%20who%20are%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20the%20future%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2F