%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20so%20easy%20to%20have%20a%20credit%20card%20with%20no%20annual%20fee%20that%20earns%202%25%20back%20on%20every%20purchase%2C%20like%20the%20Citi%20Double%20Cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20most%20people%20only%20have%20one%20or%20two%20cards%20in%20their%20wallet%2C%20with%20the%20default%20on%20both%20clocking%20in%20at%20just%201%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20buying%20something%20that%20isn't%20in%20a%20bonus%20category%20on%20one%20of%20your%20cards%2C%20then%20you%20should%20always%20be%20able%20to%20fall%20back%20on%20a%20default%20card%20that%20earns%20at%20least%202%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%20Not%20putting%20in%20effort%20and%20wasting%20points%20on%20low-value%20redemptions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20return%20you%20can%20get%20for%20your%20points%20is%20on%20the%20rewards%20that%20take%20some%20effort%20to%20understand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20flying%20First%20Class%20on%20a%20flight%20to%20Asia%20that%20costs%20%2420%2C000%20or%20more%20might%20not%20have%20been%20on%20your%20list%2C%20you%20can%20often%20use%20rewards%20points%20to%20get%20a%20redemption%20using%20a%20transfer%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCkrRPwage14%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCkrRPwage14%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20In